### Login as demo user
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "Password123"
}

### Product listing
GET http://localhost:4000/products?page=1&limit=6&sortBy=rating&sortOrder=desc

### Search products
GET http://localhost:4000/products/search?q=wireless

### Product detail
GET http://localhost:4000/products/prod-headphones-001

### Home recommendations
GET http://localhost:4000/recommendations/home/demo-user

### Product recommendations
GET http://localhost:4000/recommendations/product/prod-headphones-001

### User recommendations
GET http://localhost:4000/recommendations/user/user-1
